thread.title: Kelly & Julian
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Kelly & Julian

author: Kelly & Julian
title: Kelly & Julian
text: Working with Michelle and her team from Nelson Alexander was an absolute joy from beginning to end of our campaign. Nothing was ever too much trouble and their expert advice and professionalism was so reassuring. We had a lot of anxiety and uncertainty around the sale of our property which had significant hurdles to overcome but through Michelle's advice we were able to generate fantastic interest and make the sale at auction for well above our expectations. Michelle's consistent, professional and diligent work ethic, coupled with her lovely manner, made all the difference and we could not recommend her highly enough. Thank you
